<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Konfirmasi Penolakan</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 480px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-top: 5px solid #d9534f;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100px;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for padding */
            transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        textarea:focus {
            border-color: #ce1e10;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(206, 30, 16, 0.15);
            outline: none;
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #ce1e10;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #b0190d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Alfamart-Emblem.png" alt="Logo Perusahaan" class="logo">
            <h1>Konfirmasi Penolakan</h1>
            <p>Silakan berikan alasan mengapa permintaan untuk Nomor Ulok <strong><%= ulok %></strong> ditolak.</p>
            
            <form action="/approval/submit-rejection" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="gas_url" value="<%= gas_url %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="row" value="<%= row %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="approver" value="<%= approver %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="ulok" value="<%= ulok %>">
                <textarea name="reason" placeholder="Tuliskan alasan penolakan di sini..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Kirim Penolakan</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>